{"tid":1690943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日罷工","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T19:05:13.000Z","uid":87967,"like":29,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d996d3fbe2feb581e5b55943fe664ba51fafb2","tid":1690943,"uid":87967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"咁嘅時勢，出親街都會俾popo射/打、俾藍絲斬，搞到皮膚灼傷、耳仔脫落、眼睛失明，你真係夠膽聽日扮無事繼續返工??就算真係聽朝起身咩都無記得，你又會唔會驚自己返工途中俾人打、俾狗拉??<br />\n<br />\n正式呼籲，由於香港以家極度不安全，所有擔心自己/屋企人人身安全嘅香港人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即日罷工</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">直至緝拿所有721白衫人、其他罔顧他人安全以及有意圖襲擊平民嘅暴徒為止</span>。最重要嘅係，即時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊</span></span>，還社會寧靜，唔好再要市民承受濫權濫捕嘅危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時構思係:<br />\n由於時間緊逼，聽日朝早7-9點黨鐵不合作運動，呼籲更多人參與罷工，遍地開花<br />\n10-12點喺自己公司附近快閃遊行，地點包括: 中環、觀塘、荃灣、旺角、沙田等，詳細地點由各區統籌<br />\n3點遮打集會<br />\n<br />\n時間唔多，遊行集會有詳情後出文宣，諗到咩下面討論"},{"pid":"e7284ccb02add2d3198973db507ac8d69b043cdb","tid":1690943,"uid":204888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<br />\n香港人！罷工啦！"},{"pid":"7d31a536b7157c4fb160d1d1a0de7f5455833e52","tid":1690943,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"b0044aee4e603f68dbedb1b16c4963501de8e5ca","tid":1690943,"uid":120631,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"Call得咁急，就算有人罷都只係少數人<br />\n做唔到效果<br />\n要搞三罷要時間宣傳同準備<br />\n我都好想即刻罷得成<br />\n但以往經驗，臨時搞嘅都係失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088037b04a21270f71ec70b028239ad24a407828","tid":1690943,"uid":285030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"罷工呀！！"},{"pid":"574c82b762b4937c5b7c81128bd0e89a22f012a6","tid":1690943,"uid":40666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"你要香港人罷工無可能<br />\n你要搞到佢地無工開&gt;社會運作唔到<br />\n咁先有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524639972b4004f17183fefa96953d3fd1d0808","tid":1690943,"uid":9116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"係就搞一次有規模既罷工，一日突發可以有咩用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係要搞我都會罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c705ced85512cde95dd67fb135f528297b87afb","tid":1690943,"uid":131101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a92047b54cbcf504de46e7f44b84904c0a7e26f5","tid":1690943,"uid":54158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6e3bcb79da2807ac181072b9a8755153cce4e22","tid":1690943,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"過往經驗 呢啲叫請假打仗(打仗可能高估咗)<br />\n罷一日無意思"},{"pid":"1ca17edfb68a1377b3c043f250b45233d46099ba","tid":1690943,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"有手足被界頸 插肺 再咬甩耳仔好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日起身返工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6def26d38282c6ed10c880c3798b1f7251a20643","tid":1690943,"uid":30367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"f861ee75c343af2fea5465109e7df3353ec83d7c","tid":1690943,"uid":48448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"721 831 101<br />\n支持"},{"pid":