到post幫手推下再叫埋同事朋友老細聽日做個快閃，之後幾日多咗人再搞大佢"},{"pid":"532abd3461624177bf147e50bfbe4947a80f9fec","tid":1690943,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"唔要 : 推！<br />\n試著說 : 我要罷工！<br />\n將罷工融入日常同口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要罷工！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！</span><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51675f47b3d56d018000624466b40063e6b1a1a1","tid":1690943,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca17edfb68a1377b3c043f250b45233d46099ba","tid":1690943,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"有手足被界頸 插肺 再咬甩耳仔好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日起身返工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"劏肚呀,手根,腳根,tg燒背"},{"pid":"c24f13cdb4fd5da4d324ca96e1e63c0b1d82f711","tid":1690943,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">必須立即坐言起行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"fon